NAME
    App::WeaverUtils - Collection of CLI utilities for Pod::Weaver

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.02 of App::WeaverUtils (from Perl
    distribution App-WeaverUtils), released on 2014-12-28.

DESCRIPTION
    This distribution provides several command-line utilities related to
    Pod::Weaver.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/App-WeaverUtils>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-App-WeaverUtils>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=App-WeaverUtils>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

